src/lib/components/InsightChecklist.reac.description:
Checklist is a component that encapsulates several checkboxes.
The values and labels of the checklist is specified in the `options`
property and the checked items are specified with the `value` property.
Each checkbox is rendered as an input with a surrounding label.

value.name: string
value.description:
The value of the checkbox. This value
corresponds to the items specified in the
`value` property.

disabled.name: bool
disabled.description: If true, this checkbox is disabled and can't be clicked on.

ulStyle.description: The style of the <ul> container element

ulClassName.description: The class of the <ul> container element

inputStyle.description: The style of the <input> checkbox element

inputClassName.description: The class of the <input> checkbox element

labelStyle.description:
The style of the <label> that wraps the checkbox input
 and the option's label

labelClassName.description:
The class of the <label> that wraps the checkbox input
 and the option's label

setProps.description: Dash-assigned callback that gets fired when the value changes.

src/lib/components/InsightFoldable.react.description:
An element that can be hidden by clicking on the `title`
element. The `value` text is shown when hidden, otherwise
`children` are displayed.

title.description: The title of the item (click this to toggle)

titleStyle.description: The style of the <h4> title element

titleClassName.description: The class of the <h4> title element

titleFoldedClassName.description: The class of the <h4> title element when folded

titleUnfoldedClassName.description: The class of the <h4> title element when unfolded

valueStyle.description: The style of the <h5> value element - shown if main element is hidden

valueClassName.description: The class of the <h5> value element - shown if main element is hidden

setProps.description: Dash-assigned callback that gets fired when the value changes.
